description: Passengers on a visiting Norwegian cruise ship clean up two beaches in the south of the Isle of Man.
title: Cruise ship holiday makers tackle Manx beach litter
title_page: Cruise ship holiday makers tackle Manx beach litter - BBC News
maintext: Passenger Julie Christiansen, from Oslo, said: "We have the same problem of pollution so it's really nice to see the beach and help clean up a bit as well."
